data.description: Tucked away off of Gleason Drive, Williamsburg Manor will be your new home oasis! This stately townhome is ready for move-in, with a floor plan that flows for entertaining and a kitchen for the gourmet in your house. Sparkling hardwood floors fill the main level including the kitchen, living room and dining room which are all open. Kitchen is equipped w/SS appliances, glass tile backsplash, beautiful granite tops w/several work areas and breakfast bar, and walk-in pantry. Living room has plenty of space for relaxing by the fireplace and the dining room is large enough for your dinner parties! The screened porch was an upgrade during construction and provides plenty of room for you and your guests. Upstairs provides you with 3 generous bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms and a separate laundry room. Primary bedroom features an en suite bathroom with whirlpool tub and walk-in shower. Landscaping and exterior maintenance are included with HOA dues. The location is ideal for access to shopping in the Northshore/Pellissippi and Kingston Pike/S. Peters areas. Less than 20 min to UT, 20 min to airport and 30 min to ORNL!
